def get_month_payments():
    today = timezone.now().date()
    month_start = today.replace(day=1)
    return Payments.objects.filter(create_date__date__gte=month_start, create_date__date__lte=today).count()

def export_users_to_xlsx(filename):
    workbook = openpyxl.Workbook()
    sheet = workbook.active
    sheet.title = 'Users'
    sheet.append(['Telegram ID', 'Имя пользователя', 'Имя'])
    users = User.objects.all()
    for user in users:
        sheet.append([user.tg_id, user.tg_username, user.name])
    workbook.save(filename)
